title: Chihuahua
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small eatery set up for takeaway with a few stool seating, in the centre of Vigevano. Offers Tex-Mex food like fajitas, burritos, quesadilla, tacos and nachos. Pizza as well. Could choose tofu and soy chilli ans ask to omit cheese and sour cream.
